metadata.description: The favorable sunflowers was contaminated and turned into the crazy Geographers which is one of the evil monsters that adventurers with ranged attacks would love to bully. But be careful when you pass them, it’s not good to get bitten by them!

card_data.name: Geographer Card
card_data.effect: When the wearer is an Acolyte, ＋20% damage reduction against Demon and Undead

metadata.description: The half-naked, half-bird subhuman monster likes to captive the weak-minded adventurers (especially male) to become its slave with its attractive body and magical voice! Never face this beautiful demon alone if you’re not quite sure you can beat it!!
The Fiery Deviruchi has been affected by the heat of lava for years and got the power of flame, but it’s still like a mischievous kid. Be careful, don’t ever get poked to the butt by its firing fork!
It is said the teddy bear was loved by an aristocratic young lady in ancient times. After being discarded, the bear gradually had its own soul and wanted to know its master, wandering year by year.

It's just a gift box. Yes, Just a gift box. Humans~ They know it seems to be strange, but just cannot stop touching. When they find out it's actually a Chest Monster, It's just too late~

card_data.name: Myst Case Card
card_data.effect: Each attack to monsters restores 10 points of SP, this effect is triggered every 5 seconds at most.

metadata.description: The clown doll is made of delicate gears in a surprisingly complex way. Even experts have confirmed that it is not actuated by magic power! It can roll on balls depending on an excellent sense of balance. It is said that it was actually an ice cream maker in ancient times...

Investigator W said, "the red-nosed Rudolph suddenly became crazy... We had to run away from the frightful snow and frost..." Investigator M said, "we still need to investigate the reason why the mount of the great person turned into such a scary figure and took action alone... That's it..."
It is said the teddy bear was loved by an aristocratic young lady in ancient times. After being discarded, the bear gradually had its own soul and wanted to know its master, wandering year by year.
The elf from the alien world. The elf is arranged to produce presents for innocent children. It represents red, the major color of an important festival. The favorite dessert: Tabala Mamasu.

Highland Parasite, who thinks she’s the most beautiful monster of Einbroch Field, doesn’t like human beings to call her “Highland”. She decides to teach these upright-walking creatures a lesson. If the Monster Laboratory called her Perlis the Rose at first, then nothing would have happened now.

The monster that perches in lava zone became very aggressive after its land was polluted by human beings. Its mane are burning flames, and it’s a dangerous guy which can quickly chase its prey on the boiling ground that human can’t even lay their foot on.

The soldier is made of delicate gears in a surprisingly complex way. Even experts have confirmed that it is not actuated by magic power! Though assembled weapons are toys, it is reported that they can hurt adventurers...

A dangerous man who led monsters to attack adventurers frequently in the Clock Tower Labyrinth in recent years, claiming himself to be one of the three alchemists who created the Clock Tower Labyrinth.
The stuffed bear that Alice, a mysterious girl, Loves most. Don't look at the bear's eyes. Though it seems to be cute, it is, After all, a confused monster.

The elegant monster in the shape of a giant wolf always wanders on the field covered with snow in the alien world. Scales of ice as clear as crystals cover the entire body of the monster. Anyone intruding on its territory will be punished at absolute zero.

card_data.name: Hatii Card
card_data.effect: When launching auto attacks, Caster has a 50% chance to freeze the enemy for 5 seconds

metadata.description: The elf that can control dolls and has always been a puzzle. The elf is confirmed by Adventurer's Guild that it can use magic of various types. "Do not be deceived by its appearance and never provoke it please. " written by injured Rafini.

The small animal born with gagteeth are originally fond of living underground, but someday it heard human beings are making fun of it. “Ah--”, the Martin screams, and it comes out of the hole angrily, declaring a war to the passing adventurers with its rounded belly.
A strange creature that can only be seen in the area which time and space are in chaos. The big eyeballs all over its body are said to be able to see through the past and the future.
